::KitKat::

She turned her head and looked at the two bots. She let out a low growl. She 
didn't like any bot who went around talking about themselves like these two 
bots were.  She thought thier egos were bigger than thier brains.  She 
turned back to Quickstrike. "These two 'tin-horns' as you call them, they 
any good or have they not had the oppertunity to prove themselves yet?" She 
leaned forward and whispered to Quickstrike, "How on Cybertron do we end up 
with bots like these?"

---Original Message----
From: THECODE  <thecode@p...>
Date: Tue Jul 4, 2000 7:57pm
Subject: Re: Neo Beast Wars

Sinister walked up to Quickstrike.

"Your beast mode, you made a good choice, totally cool! I have a scorpion
Beast Mode, nad you are half of a scorpion, so we both have scorpions! For
the thinking impared, that means we are both the same animal with the
exception that you have snake in you!" Sinister said.

"Well, actually, Sinister, there was a prehistoric Scorpion that lived
underwater and was 10 feet long millions of years ago, that's where your
beast mode came from, Sinister!" Sinesis said.

"Yeah, and you beast mode...came from the past too." Sinister pointed both
fingers at Sinesis.

"Yeah, we're rad!" Sinesis said. Clearly their egos were going to their
heads....
